{
  "stem": "8.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I, I jumped over this fence, and I carried my grandfather down this hill on my back and took him to, to the place where they were assigned to.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather had suffered, previously, several strokes, and he was very weak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was not quite conscious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was in and out of consciousness.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when we got him down there, he asked me, where are we?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I could not explain to him where we were [BACKGROUND NOISE] because he could not understand it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so finally, I said to him, you know, this is the times before the coming of the Messiah, and you know that, that before the coming of the Messiah, people go through a lot of difficulties and suffering.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he somehow calmed down with that and was able to accept it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were suffering a lot, these old people who had no one to take care of them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And mostly I think the fact that we didn't know what was going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We paid the Hungarians gendarmes some money, and they gave us some news about what was coming.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said that we would be taken to a camp where we would be fed and we would work, and the-- and the older people will be taking care of the younger children.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now one day-- it was about 10 or 11 days after we had left there-- we were told to get our belongings together and go up on the hill.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were put into the wagons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were squeezed in about 100 people into the wagon.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was not with my grandparents, but I was with my mother in the same wagon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Train car wagons, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
